ndim-utils - ndim's utility collection
Miscellaneous utilities I wrote for me.

Copyright (C) 2004 Hans Ulrich Niedermann

I build and install it as follows:

/======================================================================\

	./autogen.mk
	./configure \
		--prefix="$HOME/root/ndim-utils" \
		--enable-maintainer-mode
	make
	make install

\======================================================================/
